{"tid":1616591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴黎有刀手襲警員 至少四名警員死亡","createTime":"2019-10-03T13:09:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T16:16:37.000Z","uid":123920,"like":732,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":129,"replies":[{"pid":"ad049b6f8d4e43ab39755786688ef1dc679c9845","tid":1616591,"uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:09:48.000Z","msg":"法國巴黎周四有一名刀手在警察總部內行兇，有數名警員受傷，其中四名警員傷重死亡，刀手則在現場被擊斃。有報道指，行兇的刀手是在警察總部內工作的人員，暫未知行兇原因。<br />\n案發在當地時間下午一時左右。基於保安理由，巴黎警察總部附近的地鐵站已經關閉，法國內政部長正前往現場處理事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191003/60114115\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191003%2F60114115&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEs0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=c3ce6964\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191003%2F60114115&h=f4f74117\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191003/60114115</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b46f95f5e0187bd51abde60224a4c8402bcd2ee","tid":1616591,"uid":107212,"like":78,"dislike":6,"score":72,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:10:26.000Z","msg":"學野啦！"},{"pid":"2768519ed9adb6b7805eb200f12c5c187ea07a47","tid":1616591,"uid":63117,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:10:39.000Z","msg":"wow"},{"pid":"c1d168bcd47044aac7a2b7b7aaeac2b7a26c5bdb","tid":1616591,"uid":253418,"like":16,"dislike":54,"score":-38,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:11:09.000Z","msg":"乜都要學法國?"},{"pid":"d18a6b2817ae0197cab8a152ee35a999c7a5aaac","tid":1616591,"uid":123920,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"